                <h3 class="text-center">What Am I Doing Now?</h3>
                    <p class="nosiderule text-center">
                     This is a <a target="_new" href="https://nownownow.com/about"/>now</a> page, inspired by<a target="_new" href="https://sive.rs/nowff"> Derek Sivers</a>, you should make one too.
                    </p>
